{"tid":1286633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返過大陸未? 呢 d 維權衝突日日都發生","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:11:01.000Z","uid":197540,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf4e8606349a683b5c323a508151733b5eabcfa","tid":1286633,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:17:45.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得毒奶?<br />\n仲記唔記得毒針?<br />\n仲記唔記得豆腐渣工程?<br />\n仲記唔記得西藏?<br />\n<br />\n發生咗咁多事，中央倒台未? 未呀嘛<br />\n如果你 expect 咁樣就可以動搖到佢地，你都未免太天真<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係真心想要幫手，你可以頂盡用幾分鐘時間幫手 share twitter/ig/youtube<br />\n<br />\n但係，唔該唔好唔記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span>，唔好畀人 spin 走！<br />\n<br />\n千析唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 籌款<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7.6 / 7.7 舉任何有關武漢相 / 口號 / 標語<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺太多感情落去住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎光環, 或者將香港遊行 link up 咗佢地"},{"pid":"bb56de017eff69864c6ed49c1eaeccd548b019c5","tid":1286633,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d77120e72b7329536b3fc655c2bf3e5d7547bf49","tid":1286633,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇野講</code>"},{"pid":"e56428b06727774bd2e9ce12c56695426899e10b","tid":1286633,"uid":